  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for all the feedback.\r\n\r\n1. You cannot bind multiple searchBox to a single container, it has been discussed multiple times but in the end the \"multi index search\" can be achieved with very little code https://jsfiddle.net/j9nwpz34/. This will become the official way in the newly done website of instantsearch.js\r\n2. Query hook has no knowledge of the index used. And a single instantsearch instance only deals with a single index.\r\n\r\nTo better understand what you want to achieve, we will need the concrete usecase rather than the implementation. In this very issue we are talking about implementations of your need but not the business/concrete usecase which we need. Getting the usecase will help us provide you maybe a better solution.",
